from dbd david davidian subject account of anti-armenian human right violation in azerbaijan account of anti-armenian human right violation in azerbaijan prelude to current event in nagorno-karabakh i ask what go on he say what the matter ca you see they overturn a car and they kill armenian deposition of zaven armenakovich badasian born employed sumgait bulk yarn plant resident at building apartment microdistrict no sumgait azerbaijan on february my wife and i go to baku to go shop and return to sumgait at around five in the even we run into one of my relative at the bu station and get to talk a lot of person have gather not far away near the store well at first we do know what wa happen and then a fellow i know come up to me an azerbaijani guy and say what be you stand here for go home immediately i ask what go on he say what the matter ca you see they overturn a car and they kill armenian he help me catch a cab and we get home safely we sit at home for two day during that time a gang of bandit come into my courtyard but the neighbor would let them in the build there be about of them they have stick and piece of armature in their hand they be shout something but you could understand it it wa one voice or two all of them be shout in a choru they turn toward building they go up to the third floor and we see that they break glas and throw thing out the window after a while they come out the entryway one ha a pair of jean in hi hand another ha a tape recorder and a third a guitar they go on toward the auto part store we have to save ourself after midnight on march we go to hide at school no which be in microdistrict there be two other armenian family there with u there be of u altogether out of all of them i have only know ernest before he have move to sumgait from kirovabad the azerbaijani guard at the school let u in at first he do want to but there wa nowhere else for u to go we have to plead with him and talk him into it we be tell that on that day the there would be an attack on my microdistrict we go upstair to a classroom on the second floor on the city radio station they announce three telephone number that could be use to summon assistance or communicate anything important i call one of them and the first secretary of the sumgait city party committee answer i ask him for assistance i say we in school no we need to be evacuate well he say got it wait there i send out help now i know hi voice the first secretary have be to my plant i have speak with him personally when i call he say muslimzade here about two hour after the call we hear shout near the school we look out the window and about to person be outside say armenian come out we here to get you they have club axe and armature shaft in their hand the guard sit there with u and ask where should i go i say if ymy life be of any value to you you go down there and say that the armenian be here and that they leave that what he do he go down there and say the armenian be here he say i let them out the back door they go that way and point with hi hand and with shout and noise the mob set off in the direction he have point so the assistance we have be promise do come they send u help all right instead of send real soldier he have send hi own i be positive that muslimzade do that no one have see u enter the school no one know that we be there in any case we stay at the school until seven in the morning and no soldier of any sort come to my aid in the morning we go to my relative in microdistrict and the soldier take u to the sk club from there the club wa jam with person and there be lot of person ahead of u there wa no space available one small boy about three month old die right in my arm there wa a single doctor nothing the boy wa uninjured there be no wind or bruise on him he wa just very ill they give him mouth-to-mouth resuscitation they do everything they could under the circumstance but be unable to save him and hi mother and father a young armenian couple be right there on the floor i search for a spot for u in the sk we have a small child of my own i want to find a room or something to put my family in i go up to the third floor there be a lot of soldier up there bandage with cane limp with their head break open they be a terrible sight young guy all of them there be a lot of bandage armenian too everyone have be beat everyone wa cry wail and call for help i think that the city party committee ignore u completely true there wa a snack bar a sausage wa kopek or kopek a package of cookie that cost kopek wa be sell for a bottle soft drink cost a ruble but there wa no way to get the thing any cheaper i meet my old uncle aram mikhailovich there he saw me and tear well up in hi eye my whole life he have tell me that we be friendly people that we work together he alway have azerbaijani over at hi house and now he saw me and there wa nothing he could say he just cry you can understand hi feel of course april yerevan reference the sumgait tragedy pogrom against armenian in soviet azerbaijan volume i eyewitnes account edit by samuel shahmuradian forward by yelena bonner publish by aristide d caratza ny page david davidian dbd armenium ha not learn a lesson in center for regional study anatolium and ha forget the box punishment inflict on it cambridge ma late turkish president turgut ozal 